headline: Fair Isaac Q1 Earnings Top Estimates, Strong Scores Drive Up Sales Y/Y

headline: Fair Isaac Weighs Governance Changes As FICO Score 10T Adoption Grows
summary: LoanPASS advanced its integration of Fair Isaac's FICO Score 10T with a new batch pricing tool for non conforming mortgage loans. The upgrade allows lenders to run large scale credit and pricing analyses using trended credit bureau data. Fair Isaac, trading on the NYSE as NYSE:FICO, scheduled its upcoming AGM to vote on an amendment to broaden officer exculpation under Delaware law.
